{"tid":1885470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"幾經波折新專輯終於出爐 IZ*ONE刷新女團銷量紀錄","createTime":"2020-02-18T10:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T02:53:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2306e5f9cab90f8687ad6cad7a9ec230b68c81a8","tid":1885470,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"人氣不減！<br />\n<br />\n由選秀節目《PRODUCE 48》中衍生的女團IZ*ONE，團體首隻正規專輯《BLOOM*IZ》原定在去年11月發行，但期間爆出節目排名造假風波，令回歸日程無奈一再拖延。成員們停工近3個月後，新專輯終於在昨日（17日）發表，不只主打曲《FIESTA》旋即登上音源榜三甲，專輯的單日銷量更打破歷代K-POP女團紀錄，證明IZ*ONE人氣仍然高企。<br />\n<br />\n據韓國專輯銷售量統計網站Hanteo Chart資料顯示，IZ*ONE於韓國時間17日下午6時發行的首張正規專輯《BLOOM*IZ》，單日總銷量約為18萬4千張，刷新了組合自身記錄，同時也是歷代K-POP女團中，首次有組合創下了18萬張以上的專輯首發單日初動銷量，超越了前輩們的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n而新專輯主打曲《FIESTA》也在韓國國內多個不同的音源網站上取得佳績，證明了組合的超高人氣和無限潛力。IZ*ONE稍後會再重新展開專輯宣傳工作，登上音樂節目、出演綜藝等，但由於疫情所限，SHOWCASE和簽名會等和粉絲有互動的活動或將有變數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eDEFolvLn0A&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeDEFolvLn0A%26feature%3Demb_title&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=0b4b00d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eDEFolvLn0A&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5931756-%E5%B9%BE%E7%B6%93%E6%B3%A2%E6%8A%98%E6%96%B0%E5%B0%88%E8%BC%AF%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-izone%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%A5%B3%E5%9C%98%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5931756-%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%258A%2598%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590-izone%25E5%2588%25B7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c5e8f9e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/artic